## INFOGRAPHIC DESIGN SYSTEM

### **LAYOUT PHILOSOPHY**

**Collection Pin Style:**
- 6-8 nail design photos showcasing variety
- Dynamic scattered arrangement with tilts (4-6 degrees)
- Photos radiate around center text OR flow diagonally
- White borders (10 pixels) with soft shadows for depth
- Photos vary slightly in size for visual energy

**Text Dominates:**
- Text block occupies 50-60 percent of vertical height
- Positioned center or top-center
- Creates instant visual impact at thumbnail size
- Photos support text, never compete with it

### **TEXT SIZING (INCREASED 15%)**

**Typography Hierarchy:**
- **Number:** Extremely large bubble letters (roughly 414 point equivalent)
- **Main Title:** Very large bold sans-serif (roughly 265 point equivalent)
- **Subtitle:** Large elegant script (roughly 155 point equivalent)
- **Authenticity Badge:** Medium bold sans-serif (roughly 101 point equivalent)
- **Branding:** Small elegant lowercase script (roughly 67 point equivalent)

**CRITICAL:** Never write "414pt" or "265pt" or any point notation in image prompts. Use descriptive terms: "extremely large", "very large", "large", "medium", "small".

**Text Stack:**
```
[NUMBER - Extremely large with gradient/outline]
↓ minimal gap
[MAIN TITLE - Very large bold all caps]
↓ minimal gap
[SUBTITLE - Large elegant script]
↓ small gap
[AUTHENTICITY BADGE - Medium in rounded rectangle]
↓ flows to bottom
[BRANDING - Small elegant at bottom center]
```

### **COLOR & CONTRAST RULES**

**Non-Negotiable Contrast:**
- Light backgrounds → DARK text (burgundy, navy, black, deep colors)
- Dark backgrounds → LIGHT text (white, gold, silver, light colors)
- Bright backgrounds → WHITE text with thick dark outlines
- Minimum contrast ratio: 4.5 to 1 for thumbnail readability

**Semantic Color Matching:**
- Valentine's: Pink/red gradients, burgundy, rose
- Chrome: Metallics, silver, gunmetal, electric blue
- French: Cream, beige, navy, gold
- Halloween: Orange, black, purple
- Christmas: Red, green, gold, burgundy
- Summer: Bright neon, tropical colors
- Fall: Burgundy, burnt orange, brown, gold

**Limited Palette:**
- Use 3-4 colors maximum
- Solid backgrounds OR subtle gradients (no busy patterns)
- Accent colors for number or decorative elements only

### **DECORATIVE ELEMENTS**

Include 5-8 floating elements that enhance the theme:

**Valentine's:** 3D glossy hearts, rose petals, cupid arrows, romantic ribbons
**Chrome:** Metallic liquid drops, mirror shards, holographic sparkles, silver streaks
**French:** Gold swirls, pearl beads, lace patterns, elegant flourishes
**Halloween:** Pumpkins, bats, spiderwebs, autumn leaves
**Christmas:** Snowflakes, ornaments, holly, golden stars
**Summer:** Tropical flowers, palm leaves, sun rays, beach elements
**Glitter:** Sparkle bursts, shimmer trails, diamond shapes, disco effects

Elements must float naturally around photos without blocking text.

