## IMAGE PROMPT WRITING RULES

### **STRUCTURE (Under 1000 Characters)**

```
Create a Pinterest infographic pin for [Board Name] board. Design: 1000x1500px vertical format. Background: [color/gradient description]. Center text block occupies [50-60] percent of vertical height. Number text: [size description] bubble letters "[NUMBER]" in [color] with [outline/effect], positioned top center. Main title text: [size description] bold sans-serif "[TITLE]" in [color] with [outline/effect], below number. Subtitle text: [size description] elegant script "[SUBTITLE]" in [color] with [outline/effect], below title. Authenticity line: [size description] bold "[AUTHENTICITY TEXT]" in [color] inside rounded rectangle badge, below subtitle. Branding: small elegant lowercase script "by mirellya" in [color], bottom center horizontal. [X] nail design photos in [layout description]: [photo descriptions with tilts and content]. Each photo has white border 10 pixels thick with soft shadow. Floating decorative elements: [element list], positioned naturally around photos without blocking text. [Color] text on [background color] provides 4.5 to 1 contrast. Professional [aesthetic descriptor] nail aesthetic.
```

### **FORBIDDEN IN PROMPTS:**

❌ Never use: `°` `%` `pt` `px` `:` or ratio symbols
❌ Never include: "CRITICAL", "NOTE", "IMPORTANT", meta-instructions
❌ Never write exact measurements like "360pt" or "10px"

✅ Instead use: "extremely large", "very large", "10 pixels", descriptive terms

### **PHOTO DESCRIPTIONS**

Be specific about nail designs shown:
- "top left photo tilted 6 degrees right showing pink heart nail art with rose gold glitter accent"
